03:48.103 --> 03:49.938
against my anger

03:48.103 --> 03:49.938
displacement tendencies.

03:49.980 --> 03:53.441
But ultimately,

03:49.980 --> 03:53.441
therapy was my decision.

03:53.483 --> 03:56.778
Not theirs... mine.

03:56.820 --> 03:59.280
It was voluntary.

03:59.322 --> 04:00.281
Okay.

04:00.323 --> 04:01.282
Yes, I am!

04:01.324 --> 04:04.244
My fear of rejection

04:01.324 --> 04:04.244
