Basically, you wash it,

04:12.878 --> 04:16.548
you dry it, you fold it.

04:16.590 --> 04:18.550
You want me to go

04:16.590 --> 04:18.550
through that again?

04:18.592 --> 04:19.885
No, twice was good.

04:19.927 --> 04:22.179
Actually, I don't mind

04:19.927 --> 04:22.179
doing laundry.

04:22.221 --> 04:24.181
Mom always thought

04:22.221 --> 04:24.181
she was punishing me,

04:24.223 --> 04:27.768
