04:38.403 --> 04:40.321
We take this crappy

04:38.403 --> 04:40.321
soap off his hands,

04:40.363 --> 04:43.242
and, uh, he makes it

04:40.363 --> 04:43.242
worth our while.

04:43.283 --> 04:45.827
The Alabama Opera?

04:45.869 --> 04:47.370
There's plenty more

04:45.869 --> 04:47.370
