04:47.412 --> 04:48.622
No thanks.

04:48.663 --> 04:50.415
Opera's not your thing.

04:50.457 --> 04:51.875
That's fine.

04:51.917 --> 04:53.794
This guy's got connections.

04:53.835 --> 04:56.880
Cords of firewood,

04:53.835 --> 04:56.880
tractor show,

04:56.922 --> 04:58.632
free burgers from Churchill's

04:56.922 --> 04:58.632
when you buy a burger

04:58.673 --> 05:00.259
