Where are my cooling racks?

05:23.782 --> 05:25.366
I know I put them in here.

05:23.782 --> 05:25.366
What a mess!

05:25.408 --> 05:26.409
Honey, please.

05:26.451 --> 05:27.619
I'll go to the store,

05:27.661 --> 05:28.662
and I'll buy you

05:27.661 --> 05:28.662
new cooling racks.

05:28.703 --> 05:30.080
No! I want to find these.

05:30.122 --> 05:31.915
And when I do, we are

05:30.122 --> 05:31.915
all going to clean out

05:31.957 --> 05:33.374
this disaster of a closet.

05:33.416 --> 05:35.127
It's going to be our

05:33.416 --> 05:35.127
new family project.

05:35.169 --> 05:37.171
We never finished our

05:35.169 --> 05:37.171
last family project.

05:37.212 --> 05:39.464
Because it's in here,

05:37.212 --> 05:39.464
under two tons of crap.

05:43.969 --> 05:45.887
Your dentist appointment, Lloyd?

05:45.929 --> 05:47.848
My teeth feel fine today,

05:45.929 --> 05:47.848
Caroline.

05:47.889 --> 05:49.891
I like myself.

05:50.934 --> 05:54.188
