07:36.497 --> 07:37.374
No.

07:37.416 --> 07:38.875
You'll just think it's stupid.

07:38.917 --> 07:42.503
Nothing you ever say in here

07:38.917 --> 07:42.503
will be stupid.

07:42.545 --> 07:44.798
But all I ever do

07:42.545 --> 07:44.798
