07:44.839 --> 07:49.261
I feel like I don't even deserve

07:44.839 --> 07:49.261
to beat my own high score.

07:49.303 --> 07:51.512
Oh, yes, you do, Malcolm.

07:51.554 --> 07:52.806
Thank you so much.

07:52.847 --> 07:55.058
The tricky part is,

07:52.847 --> 07:55.058
I need to keep this up

07:55.100 --> 07:57.227
without being put

07:55.100 --> 07:57.227
on medication.

07:58.061 --> 08:01.022
Underpants!

07:58.061 --> 08:01.022
In a closet!

08:01.064 --> 08:03.066
Human underpants!

08:03.108 --> 08:05.526
I must not

08:03.108 --> 08:05.526
