08:05.568 --> 08:07.404
Oh, my Lord.

08:07.446 --> 08:08.780
Skittles!

08:08.822 --> 08:10.615
(laughs)

08:10.657 --> 08:14.119
You've been missing

08:10.657 --> 08:14.119
