09:32.697 --> 09:34.282
I can't believe it!

09:34.324 --> 09:36.076
This collar's so crisp,

09:34.324 --> 09:36.076
yet it doesn't chafe.

09:36.117 --> 09:37.536
And these sheets...

09:37.577 --> 09:39.079
