09:39.120 --> 09:40.872
My pleasure, guys.

09:40.914 --> 09:42.416
Dude...

09:42.457 --> 09:43.166
thank you.

09:43.208 --> 09:44.292
I've been hoping

09:43.208 --> 09:44.292
