10:05.188 --> 10:06.565
Well, yeah, whatever.

10:06.606 --> 10:08.608
Guess I could find some time

10:06.606 --> 10:08.608
for your stuff.

10:09.692 --> 10:12.404
Hey... thanks, man.

10:13.572 --> 10:14.655
No, no, no, you don't have to...

10:14.697 --> 10:15.615
You're the best.

10:28.462 --> 10:29.796
Go.

10:31.005 --> 10:32.632
Ha-cha!

10:34.008 --> 10:35.843
Garbage! In a closet!

10:35.885 --> 10:37.845
Coffee grounds? Hal!

10:37.887 --> 10:39.680
Lois, you've

10:37.887 --> 10:39.680
got to see this.

10:39.722 --> 10:41.558
The boy's a prodigy. Go.

10:41.600 --> 10:42.767
Yes.

