10:45.853 --> 10:46.729
Here we go.

10:46.771 --> 10:48.689
Now.

10:48.731 --> 10:51.067
Amazing!

10:51.109 --> 10:52.735
Hi, Malcolm.

10:51.109 --> 10:52.735
How was school?

10:52.777 --> 10:54.779
It was normal.

10:54.821 --> 10:56.239
Yeah, I'd say normal.

10:56.281 --> 10:57.740
Very medieval.

10:57.782 --> 10:59.826
